---
title: Bang Bang Tofu Bowl with Edamame and Avocado
description: This Bang Bang tofu bowl is a festival of flavours! We've stepped up every element of this lively dish. From cilantro avocado salsa to sweet and spicy sriracha mayo, each colourful bite is a delight.
